{"tid":2213433,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(慎入/痴線)2020年搞笑諾貝爾獎其中一位得獎者的研究，用人類糞便製作利刀","createTime":"2020-09-22T13:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T12:07:03.000Z","uid":38861,"like":51,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a8f8c55657e3ee2b30abb7616d8b4886f5e8cf83","tid":2213433,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:41:37.000Z","msg":"整個研究的起因，某程度上來自Wade Davis作家所寫下一本名為Shadows In The Sun的書。<br />\n<br />\n書中記載一名因紐特人（Inuit Man，美洲原主民之一）利用自己的糞便和口水在寒凍製作小刀，並成功刺殺小狗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n整個故事被翻製成為記錄片及書本，得以廣泛流傳（雖然我從來無聽過依個故仔），而有一幫科學家唔太相信依個故仔，所以.......<br />\n<br />\n就做實驗測試一下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文章的頭兩位科學家分別食下各種的食物（圖1），再用痾出的糞便在攝氏零下二十度製作利刀，再擺喺負五十度的乾冰幾分鐘確保刀身結實，之後就嘗試切割豬皮驗證糞刀究竟可唔可行.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AmsmRfv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAmsmRfv.png&h=8d79ae16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文章Link: <a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S2352409X19305371?via%2525253Dihub\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS2352409X19305371%3Fvia%252525253Dihub&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I251e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=55ff4765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S2352409X19305371?via%2525253Dihub</a><br />\n<br />\n而依個研究......順利令佢哋成為今年搞笑諾貝爾獎的其中一位得獎者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔想睇圖的話，可以依家上一頁，但代價就係唔會知道結果。<br />\n<br />\n想睇糞刀的話，可以繼續拉落去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AgGSdtU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAgGSdtU.png&h=4a37586c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利用第一位者的糞便倒模後，糞刀亦得以成型。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdkjCVC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdkjCVC.png&h=2eb9e117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n磨利刀......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BOfGRfG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBOfGRfG.png&h=9bd56b2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一刀兩斷，FAIL，只能夠在豬皮上留下「到此一遊」的淺痕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鑑於可能係第一位的仁兄糞便唔夠「勁」的關係，第二位仁兄亦用自己的糞便整刀，以及一系列的打磨。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8EM3j84.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8EM3j84.png&h=5de1f40b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VBtAVHs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVBtAVHs.png&h=e92ea5ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一切就緒，要切了！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VtpO2v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VtpO2v.png&h=c5e4cafe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果係比上一位仁兄的糞刀留下更深的裂痕，但切割之後作者表示刀鋒有融解的跡象........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最終佢哋得出的結果就係，利用人類糞便製作利刀係唔可行的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c2cfe9f00c46511440fa5589b8beeadb17b260","tid":2213433,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5b46192ebd32d57b3c2c61c67e98370ff035e0","tid":2213433,"uid":58642,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:44:06.000Z","msg":"好玩唔玩玩屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66c6448ac0b6bf83abe032b17433ed6c219e83d","tid":2213433,"uid":38861,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2f5b46192ebd32d57b3c2c61c67e98370ff035e0","tid":2213433,"uid":58642,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:44:06.000Z","msg":"好玩唔玩玩屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:45:46.000Z","msg":"完整標題：（慎入/痴線）2020年搞笑諾貝爾獎其中一位得獎者的研究，用人類糞便整刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />玩屎玩到攞獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb159113807626ad89a5d046552ca903a476aa27","tid":2213433,"uid":59922,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:48:39.000Z","msg":"研究精神係咁，除咗笑之外，真係要佩服"},{"pid":"afbd3d6211421af5cca126280d8a642dcde6594f","tid":2213433,"uid":199689,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:49:54.000Z","msg":"可能係diet嘅問題<br />\n如果食樹皮就分分鐘得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b714d86fe24e97e2981baedb489ae1c3c621797","tid":2213433,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bc29375816941b01225bb48b49356e75ba16ad","tid":2213433,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb159113807626ad89a5d046552ca903a476aa27","tid":2213433,"uid":59922,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:48:39.000Z","msg":"研究精神係咁，除咗笑之外，真係要佩服"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/p